article.description: — Joe Anderson's 19 points helped Lipscomb defeat Bellarmine 81-70 on Saturday night.
article.headline: Anderson scores 19, Lipscomb defeats Bellarmine 81-70
article.story: LOUISVILLE, Ky. -- — Joe Anderson's 19 points helped Lipscomb defeat Bellarmine 81-70 on Saturday night. Anderson added seven assists and three steals for the Bisons (10-7, 1-1 Atlantic Sun Conference). Derrin Boyd scored 14 points, shooting 5 for 11 (1 for 5 from 3-point range) and 3 of 3 from the free throw line. A.J McGinnis was 4 of 9 shooting (4 for 8 from 3-point range) to finish with 14 points. Ben Johnson finished with 16 points for the Knights (4-13, 0-2). Garrett Tipton added 13 points for Bellarmine. Langdon Hatton also had 12 points and six rebounds. The loss was the Knights' sixth straight. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
